                      On the eve of my jersey retirement, It only makes sense to bring the city together for a pickup game at Simeon. A light run that celebrates the rich history of Chicago basketball.<br aria-hidden="true" />
                      A history that doesn't exist without you.<br aria-hidden="true" />
                      Let's hoop!<br aria-hidden="true" />
                      <br aria-hidden="true" />
                      Peace and Love,<br aria-hidden="true" />
                      Pooh</span>
                      <span class="hidden md:inline">We all know Chicago hoopers are built different. From playgrounds to packed gyms, The Southside to out West, our grit and toughness have never been denied.<br />
                      <span>Not then. Not now. </span>
                      <span>Not ever. We are </span>
                      <span class="font-roboto-condensed font-bold">Homegrown.</span><br /><br />
                      On the eve of my jersey retirement, it only makes sense to bring the city together for a pickup game at Simeon.<br>A light run that celebrates the rich history of Chicago basketball.<br />A history that doesn't exist without you.<br />Let's <span class="font-roboto-condensed font-normal">hoop!</span><br />
                      <br />Peace and Love,<br />
                      Pooh</span>
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <!-- What You Get Section -->
